{"id":"811804701955915776","type":"text","timestamp":1774197294,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/811804701955915776","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/sapphic-dice/810994736756391936\">sapphic-dice</a>:</p><blockquote><p>I like being me.</p><p><br/></p><p>That’s kinda it.</p><p>That felt important.</p><p><br/></p><p><small>If I stop worrying about needing to be useful for others, about not being a burden… as hard as that is to do… I like who I am.</small></p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"sapphic-dice"},"post":{"id":"810994736756391936"}}],"baseline_notes":90,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}